label: A4BC3_oF64_69_gho_g_gl-001
title: LaTi$_{3}$Bi$_{4}$ Structure
comments:
In orthorhombic systems the AFLOW prototype label standard favors orientations of where most of the free atomic parameters are along the x-axis.  Thus we have rotated the published structure so that coordinates (x,y,z) $\rightarrow$ (z,y,-x), with a similar change for the lattice parameters. 
 The ICSD lists Nd(Sb,Sn)$_{3}$Bi$_{4}$ as the prototype for this structure, but we prefer to use a fully ordered structure.
